      "text": "linux_exporter  (node_exporter)\ncustomer Linux hosts  \u2022  port :9100\n\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\u2500\nAdd: 'add linux_exporter target <ip:9100> with hostname <name>'\nShips empty out of the box",
