      "y": 158,
      "width": 1034,
      "height": 114,
      "text": "Loki  \u2022  v3.2.0\nListens on  :3100 (HTTP)  \u2022  :9096 (gRPC)\nretention_period  2160h (90d)  \u2022  compactor  in-process  \u2022  compaction_interval 10m  \u2022  reject_old_samples 168h\nStorage: /loki volume  \u2022  filesystem chunks + boltdb-shipper index  \u2022  config: config/loki.yml",
